item.description:

Questions
4. Done in player.java for starting place find // initial x and y coordinates of the player and change the teleportToX and teleportToY then for what they’re wearing find //Giving the player an unique look and under that change the items after each thing to what you want them to be wearing

7. Add a sendquest under refreshsummonbook to change what it says … it would be sendQuest("", 174);
